		15.	Also encourage Parties that have already reported on the social and economic consequences of response measures to continue and enhance such reporting in both a qualitative and a quantitative manner;
		16.	Request the secretariat to prepare a synthesis report on the information on response measures reported by Parties in their biennial transparency reports and present it to the Katowice Committee on Impacts at its 13th meeting.

